node.title: Truck crashes into houses in West Auckland
node.description: A truck has crashed into two houses in Titirangi and the driver has been taken to hospital in a serious condition.
node.content:
["A truck has crashed into two houses in west Auckland and the driver has been taken to hospital in a serious condition.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf.com\n
", "The crash happened on Golf Road, Titirangi, just before 8.30am.", "There were no immediate reports of injuries to people at either house."]
